---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About - Neon Injector"
  description="Learn about Neon Injector, our mission, journey, and how we enhance your Mobile Legends experience with safe and seamless skin customization."
>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <main class="flex-1 pt-16">
      <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-[var(--text-color)]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neon-purple mb-8 text-center">About Neon Injector</h1>
        <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <p class="mb-6">Neon Injector is a cutting-edge tool designed to enhance your Mobile Legends experience by enabling safe, seamless, and purely cosmetic skin customizations on Android devices. Since our inception in 2023, we have been dedicated to providing players with a reliable and user-friendly way to personalize their favorite heroes' appearances without affecting gameplay fairness.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">At Neon Injector, our mission is to empower Mobile Legends players with innovative tools to express their creativity through custom skins. We strive to combine advanced technology with a passion for gaming, ensuring our tool is secure, accessible, and compatible with the latest Android devices and Mobile Legends updates. Our goal is to enhance your gaming experience while maintaining respect for the game's integrity.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Our Journey</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">Founded by a group of passionate Mobile Legends players and developers, Neon Injector has evolved from a small project into a globally recognized tool trusted by thousands of players. Our key milestones include:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li><strong>2023</strong>: Launched Neon Injector v1.0, introducing basic skin injection capabilities for Mobile Legends players.</li>
            <li><strong>Mid-2024</strong>: Implemented support for Storage Access Framework (SAF) and Shizuku, enhancing security and compatibility with modern Android systems.</li>
            <li><strong>Early 2025</strong>: Released Neon Injector v2.3.1, featuring a faster injection process, an expanded skin library, and improved user interface for seamless navigation.</li>
            <li><strong>Ongoing</strong>: Continuous updates to ensure compatibility with Mobile Legends patches and active engagement with our community through feedback channels.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Why Choose Neon Injector?</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">Neon Injector stands out as a trusted tool for Mobile Legends players due to its robust features and commitment to user satisfaction. Hereâ€™s why players choose us:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Universal Compatibility</strong>: Works on all Android devices running version 7.0 or higher, with support for both rooted and non-rooted devices.</li>
            <li><strong>Frequent Updates</strong>: Regular patches to align with Mobile Legends updates, ensuring uninterrupted skin customization.</li>
            <li><strong>Community-Driven</strong>: We actively engage with our users through our <a href="https://discord.gg/neoninjector" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Discord server</a> and blog, incorporating feedback to improve the tool.</li>
            <li><strong>Comprehensive Support</strong>: Detailed <a href="/docs" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">documentation</a> and responsive support via <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">contact channels</a> to assist with setup and troubleshooting.</li>
            <li><strong>Safe and Ethical</strong>: Our tool focuses on cosmetic changes only, avoiding any modifications that could affect gameplay fairness or violate ethical gaming standards.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Join the Neon Injector Community</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">Ready to elevate your Mobile Legends experience with stunning custom skins? Download Neon Injector today and join thousands of players worldwide who trust us for their skin customization needs. Visit our <a href="/download" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Download page</a> to get started, or reach out to our team via the <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact page</a> for any questions or support.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>